title: Librivox Cocoa Break Collection, Vol. 02
creator: Various
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Librivox Cocoa Break Collection, Vol. 02 by Various Authors. Read by LibriVox Volunteers This is a collection of international fairy tales clocking in at 5-15 minutes apiece, suitable for childrens' winter cocoa breaks, or other times when quality entertainment is needed. (Summary by BellonaTimes) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
